---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Home | ScoutFox" pageClass="garden-theme">
  <h1>ScoutFox</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Intelligent monitoring for the signals that matter.</p>

  <section class="card">
    <p>
      The web constantly produces signals that influence decisions: new
      technologies, market shifts, regulatory changes, and research
      breakthroughs.
    </p>
    <p>
      Most of these signals appear quietly across scattered sources and are
      easy to miss.
    </p>
    <p>
      ScoutFox monitors the web contextually and surfaces the signals that
      matter before they become obvious.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Momentum</h2>
    <p>Built during the Lossfunk residency (Jan-Feb 2026).</p>
    <p>Winner of the OSS4AI February Hackathon.</p>
    <p>Currently developed in the TinyFish accelerator program.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Now</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Building ScoutFox in the TinyFish accelerator</li>
      <li>Exploring intelligent web monitoring systems</li>
      <li>Researching signal detection and decision intelligence</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="card">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <p><strong>ScoutFox</strong> - Intelligent web monitoring system</p>
    <p>Lossfunk Residency Project (2026)</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Founder Thesis</h2>
    <p>
      I'm building systems that surface the signals humans need to make better
      decisions.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
